description:
The Dragon was ranked 4th overall last season with 18 amazing submissions. In her lifetime stats she has accumulated over 1500 style points. She has trained in the off-season and want to regain the championship.
The Jester was ranked 8th overall last season with 0 submissions. With 5 matches under her belt the learning is over, it is time to show US what you have.
title: The Dragon(0-0) The Jester(0-0)
